# Build context for every app Dockerfile is the monorepo root, so Docker
# reads THIS file (a `.dockerignore` inside apps/<app>/ is ignored when
# the context is the root — classic Docker only honours
# `<context>/.dockerignore`, and BuildKit's per-Dockerfile variant must
# be named `Dockerfile.dockerignore`). This file therefore serves
# apps/api, apps/web, and apps/console builds alike.
#
# Keep this list aligned with `.gitignore`. When in doubt, add an entry
# here and to `.gitignore` together.

# ----- mirrors .gitignore -----
**/node_modules
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.js
**/.pnpm-store
**/.yarn
**/.npm

**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/.next
**/.next-e2e
**/.turbo
**/.swc
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/storybook-static

# Prisma 7 generated client — a build artefact regenerated inside the
# builder stage (ADR-0041); never copy the host's local copy.
packages/db/src/generated

# Foundry / Solidity (app images never read these but they're large)
**/cache
**/broadcast
**/artifacts
**/typechain-types
packages/contracts/lib

# Tests / coverage
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/*.lcov
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/playwright/.cache

# Env + secrets — never bake into an image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# AWS / wallet artefacts
**/.aws
aws-exports.js
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/private-key*
**/keystore
**/wallet.json

# Terraform never belongs in app images
infra
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/*.tfvars
**/.terraform
**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# OS / IDE noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea
**/*.iml
**/.vscode
**/.cursor
**/.history

# Logs
**/*.log
**/logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-*.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# Misc tarballs / deploy artefacts
**/*.tgz
**/*.tar.gz
**/.vercel
**/.netlify
**/.serverless

# ----- build-time-only -----
**/.git
.github
docs
**/README.md
!packages/db/README.md
!apps/api/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md

# Local docker overrides
docker-compose.override.yml
local.config.*
